<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.4">
<l>epporuḷun tāṉāy marakatak kuṉṟamokku</l>
<l>mappoḻutai tāmaraippū kaṇpātaṅ kaikamala</l>
<l>meppoḻutu nāṭiṅka ḷāṇṭūḻi yūḻitoṟu</l>
<l>mappoḻutaik kappoḻuteṉ ṉārā vamutamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who, being every thing, resembles an emerald mountain,</l>
<l>the lord of that time [has] lotus flowers eyes, hand [and] feet lotusses.</l>
<l>All the times, day, month, year, aeon after aeon,</l>
<l>those times [are] those times of the lord, my never-sating ambrosia.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
